    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable wear including visible scratches and minor dents, with some paint fading. The interior has evident wear on the upholstery and trim consistent with regular use. Mechanically functional, but this car will likely require some attention and repairs. Priced accordingly for its condition.",
